---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Affiliate Disclosure" description="How Aveliq uses affiliate links and maintains editorial independence.">
  <section class="simple-page">
    <div class="simple-hero">
      <div class="simple-eyebrow">Legal</div>
      <h1 class="simple-h1">Affiliate Disclosure.</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="simple-body">

      <div class="policy-block">
        <h2>What Affiliate Links Are</h2>
        <p>Some links on Aveliq are affiliate links. If you click one and subscribe to or purchase a product, Aveliq may earn a commission — at no additional cost to you. These commissions help fund our independent coverage.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="policy-block">
        <h2>Editorial Independence</h2>
        <p>Affiliate relationships never determine our coverage. Recommendations are based on real testing, documented features, and verifiable data — not on which programs pay the most. When a product is the best fit, we say so. When it isn't, we say that too.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="policy-block">
        <h2>Real Data Only</h2>
        <p>Comparison tables and product details on Aveliq are built from real, sourced information — official pricing pages, documentation, and hands-on testing. We do not invent figures, fabricate statistics, or quote sources that do not exist.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="policy-block">
        <h2>How to Identify Affiliate Links</h2>
        <p>Affiliate links carry the <code>rel="sponsored"</code> attribute and are marked where they appear. Any article containing affiliate links includes a clear disclosure at the top.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="policy-block">
        <h2>Contact</h2>
        <p>Questions about our affiliate practices? Contact <a href="mailto:hello@aveliq.net">hello@aveliq.net</a></p>
        <p style="margin-top:16px;font-size:12px;opacity:.4">Last updated: June 2026</p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
.simple-hero {
  background: var(--bg2);
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--b);
  padding: 60px 40px 48px;
}
.simple-eyebrow {
  font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
  font-size: 9px;
  letter-spacing: .14em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--amber);
  margin-bottom: 16px;
}
.simple-h1 {
  font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
  font-size: clamp(48px, 7vw, 88px);
  line-height: .95;
  letter-spacing: .02em;
  color: var(--paper);
}
.simple-body {
  max-width: 800px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  padding: 48px 40px 80px;
}
.policy-block {
  padding: 32px 0;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--b);
}
.policy-block h2 {
  font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
  font-size: 24px;
  letter-spacing: .02em;
  color: var(--paper);
  margin-bottom: 14px;
}
.policy-block p {
  font-family: 'Libre Baskerville', serif;
  font-size: 15px;
  color: rgba(245,240,232,.6);
  line-height: 1.8;
}
.policy-block a {
  color: var(--amber);
  border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(212,168,83,.3);
}
.policy-block code {
  font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
  font-size: 13px;
  color: var(--amber);
  background: var(--bg2);
  padding: 2px 6px;
}
@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .simple-hero { padding: 40px 20px 32px; }
  .simple-body { padding: 32px 20px 60px; }
}
</style>